# Security Headers
/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fareharbor.com https://www.googletagmanager.com https://assets.mailerlite.com https://groot.mailerlite.com https://embed.tawk.to https://*.tawk.to; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com https://assets.mlcdn.com https://*.tawk.to; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com https://assets.mlcdn.com https://*.tawk.to; img-src 'self' data: https:; connect-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com https://*.mailerlite.com https://*.tawk.to wss://*.tawk.to; frame-src https://fareharbor.com https://*.tawk.to;
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()

